description: White Sands National Monument.Several trails possible, the Alkalitrack is the longest one.Great wave-like dunes of gypsum sand.Al information can be found at:http://www.nps.gov/whsa/planyourvisit/index.htm
directions: Drive to White Sands National Monument near Alamogordo.Enter the park and drive to the end of the park road, Alkali track starts here.
title: Alkali trail White Sands New Mexico
